Ester has disappeared. Hobart has disappeared. I could not care less about Velious when there's stupid bugs around like:<P>

2. Alchemy potions that don't stack when they get used before the spell. But they do stack if they get used AFTER the spell was cast on them.<P>

<B>Wyrdrana,<P>

We correct outstanding issues with nearly every patch. As much as I'm sure everyone would like to see every outstanding issue addressed in one patch, it's not realistic for us to do that. Just because we don't fix all of them in every patch, or don't reply every time they are reposted on the bug board, doesn't mean that we aren't listening.<P>

