				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="6">Twelve Days of Velious - Day Nine</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:catalyst@everlore.com">Catalyst</b></a>
				[11/30/2000-6:19:00 PM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=287769"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[1]</font></a>
				<p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2"><P>
Looks like the guys at Verant have been busy, as there's another episode of the Twelve Days of Velious. Today in the <a href="http://everquest.station.sony.com/hht/veliouslore/9th.shtml">Ninth Day</a> the group seeks shelter from the weather in a near by cave and finds a bit more than they bargained for. As always an interesting tale, including some new shots. Here's a minor gankage from the page.
<Blockquote>
The mountains are filled with dangers, as our adventurers are finding in their travels. In an attempt to escape the ravages of the frigid weather, the party has made use of various caves. They’ve come to expect each one to house one or more extremely dangerous creatures, and they have not been disappointed.
</blockquote></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
		
