<B><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/everquest/Forum2/HTML/035118.html">Enchanter pets and auto-dual wield?</a></B><P>

What we want to know now is this. Will enchanter pets be made to dual-wield automatically at the levels you mentioned, just as mage and necro, and shadowknight pets now do?<P>

